data.title: Bogan Computer Technical High School
data.text:
Create a Google Account

If you do not have a Gmail Account, you can keep your Email and create a Google Account. Follow this link and follow the prompts and you'll be part of the Google Family very soon. Parent Email Collection

Provide your Gmail or Email so that you can receive Guardian Email Summaries from Google Classroom. You will see missing work, upcoming work, and class activity.
